OL,3,CDriver dumps bags of rubbish 'because
OL,4,Ctip was closed'
OL,6,FA driver has been caught on camera
OL,7,F'throwing six bags of rubbish over a
OL,8,Fhedge' near a home in Birmingham
OL,9,Fbecause 'the tip was closed'.
OL,11,FBystander Ivan Bailey, from Great
OL,12,FBarr, Birmingham, claims the driver
OL,13,F'refused to listen' when he confronted
OL,14,Fhim.JThe footage was filmed on
OL,15,FBaltimore Road, just two miles from
OL,16,FPerry Barr Household Recycling Centre,
OL,17,Fwhich is open seven days a week after
OL,18,Fan improvement scheme earlier this
OL,19,Fyear - but does require booking.
