OL,6,FThe footage has been condemned by
OL,7,Flocal residents who said fly-tipping
OL,8,Fof this kind 'happens everywhere.'JMr
OL,9,FBailey said he even offered to help
OL,10,Fthe driver put the bags back in his
OL,11,Fcar but claims he was 'ignored.'
OL,13,FThe incident took place on June 10 and
OL,14,Fhas been reported to Birmingham City
OL,15,FCouncil.
