OL,3,CDriver dumps bags of rubbish 'because
OL,4,Ctip was closed'
OL,6,FMr Bailey said: "We told him to put
OL,7,Fthe rubbish back in his car and take
OL,8,Fit home - but all he kept saying was
OL,9,F'the tip is closed'. We even offered
OL,10,Fto help him put the bags back in his
OL,11,Fcar, but he refused to listen.J"He
OL,12,Fdumped everything and drove off - the
OL,13,Frubbish is still there. We've notified
OL,14,Fthe council but there's not much else
OL,15,Fwe can do.
